sk where a career in the arts can lead.The pins represent places the professor has visited, and they show - even before Leisring became associate dean for global engagement and special performance projects for the School of Music in 2023 - that the trumpet has taken him to 20 countries on five continents.\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stephen Leisring\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 277}, {\"ngram\": \"professor\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 288}, {\"ngram\": \"trumpet\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 317}, {\"ngram\": \"Kansas\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"a map\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 350}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 363}, {\"ngram\": \"his office wall\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 382}, {\"ngram\": \"push pins\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 405}, {\"ngram\": \"prospective students\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"their parents\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"a career\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the arts\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 480}, {\"ngram\": \"The pins\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"places\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"the professor\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 529}, {\"ngram\": \"Leisring\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"associate dean\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"global engagement\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"special performance projects\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"the School\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"Music\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"the trumpet\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"20 countries\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"five continents\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not plan any of this,\\\" Leisring said.\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leisring\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It just happened through hard work and getting the right guidance.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"the right guidance\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I truly believe you can make anything happen.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 899, \"to\": 907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every generation has had to adapt.\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every generation\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if you are really passionate, you can find ways to do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A native of Connecticut and graduate of the University of North Texas and New York's Mannes School of Music, Leisring said the twig of his internationally focused career was bent when he took part in a New York City audition immediately upon earning his master's degree.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1027, \"end\": 1038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Connecticut\", \"score\": 0.9851535472014872, \"rank\": 0.015070191634048852, \"text\": \"Connecticut\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Connecticut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Connecticut\"}, {\"begin\": 1089, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999031388, \"rank\": 9.700988981259366e-11, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 1217, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5582493761587245e-17, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A native\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"graduate\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"North Texas\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"Music\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"Leisring\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"the twig\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"his internationally focused career\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"his master's degree\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won an orchestra job in the Canary Islands, which is a part of Spain located just off the coast of Africa.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9999999088586305, \"rank\": 9.110922337917406e-08, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an orchestra job\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"the Canary Islands\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"the coast\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During 14 years with theOrquesta Sinf\\u00f3nica de Tenerife, Leisring learned Spanish and taught private lessons on the side, even as the orchestra traveled around Europe performing and recording.\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tenerife\", \"score\": 0.9769933973312726, \"rank\": 0.023548224021614973, \"text\": \"Tenerife\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tenerife\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tenerife\"}, {\"begin\": 1470, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9514676751545267, \"rank\": 0.05099299947211344, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"14 years\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"Leisring\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"private lessons\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"the side\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"the orchestra\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When he returned to the states and embarked upon full-time teaching at KU in 2003, Leisring maintained and extended some of the connections he formed overseas.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1661, \"end\": 1663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Kansas\", \"score\": 0.9999999937149369, \"rank\": 6.284948664033116e-09, \"text\": \"KU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Kansas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Kansas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the states\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"full-time teaching\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"Leisring\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"the connections\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leisring was attending the annualInternational Trumpet Guildconference in May and June 2023 in Minneapolis when he met Marcos Garcia, who is a friend of a friend and who plays in the Madrid Symphony Orchestra.\", \