bpedia.org/resource/Teatro_Real\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teatro_Real\"}, {\"begin\": 2098, \"end\": 2104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Complutense_University_of_Madrid\", \"score\": 0.756156918791689, \"rank\": 0.3224768199862499, \"text\": \"Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Complutense_University_of_Madrid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Complutense_University_of_Madrid\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a three-and-a-half-week opera\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"Leisring\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In March, the group performed rarely heard works by Francis Poulenc and Arnold Schoenberg to great acclaim, he said.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2210, \"end\": 2217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_Poulenc\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Poulenc\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_Poulenc\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_Poulenc\"}, {\"begin\": 2229, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schoenberg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3572275617104934e-33, \"text\": \"Schoenberg\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schoenberg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Schoenberg\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"works\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"great acclaim\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That led, on his day off, to another gig offered to Leisring by another Spanish musician he had met in Minneapolis,David Pastor.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2340, \"end\": 2347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9514676751545267, \"rank\": 0.05099299947211344, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}, {\"begin\": 2371, \"end\": 2382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minneapolis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2425158402512655e-22, \"text\": \"Minneapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minneapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minneapolis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his day\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"another gig\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"David Pastor\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He found out I was going to be in Madrid, and I actually had a day off in between the operas,\\\" Leisring said.\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2433, \"end\": 2439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Complutense_University_of_Madrid\", \"score\": 0.756156918791689, \"rank\": 0.3224768199862499, \"text\": \"Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Complutense_University_of_Madrid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Complutense_University_of_Madrid\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a day\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"the operas\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"Leisring\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was doing a recording session with the RTVE, theRadio Television Espa\\u00f1ola, Orchestra.\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2552, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RTVE\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RTVE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RTVE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RTVE\"}, {\"begin\": 2578, \"end\": 2586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Espa\\u00f1ola,_New_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9646017889029339, \"rank\": 0.024405943249471714, \"text\": \"Espa\\u00f1ola\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Espa\\u00f1ola,_New_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Espa\\u00f1ola,_New_Mexico\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a recording session\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"Orchestra\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it was his piece.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his piece\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was the conductor.\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the conductor\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he invited me to come play first trumpet on this Olympic fanfare that he was commissioned to write.\\\"\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"first trumpet\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2687}, {\"ngram\": \"this Olympic fanfare\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only was the sound of the fanfare recorded for use in RTVE's coverage of Spain's participation in the Paris Olympics, but the musicians were recorded onvideofrom every possible angle during the long session, Leisring said, presumably for interstitial use in RTVE broadcasts.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 3027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2807, \"end\": 2811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RTVE\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RTVE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RTVE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RTVE\"}, {\"begin\": 2826, \"end\": 2831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9999999088586305, \"rank\": 9.110922337917406e-08, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}, {\"begin\": 3011, \"end\": 3015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RTVE\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RTVE\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RTVE\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RTVE\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sound\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"the fanfare\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2869}, {\"ngram\": \"the musicians\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"every possible angle\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"the long session\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2959}, {\"ngram\": \"Leisring\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2969}, {\"ngram\": \"interstitial use\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 3007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leisring said Pastor \\\"is already well known in Spain, but he's becoming really well known outside of Spain, too, because of things like these performances.\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3076, \"end\": 3081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9999999088586305, \"rank\": 9.110922337917406e-08, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}, {\"begin\": 3130, \"end\": 3135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9999999088586305, \"rank\": 9.110922337917406e-08, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leisring\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"Pastor\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3159}, {\"ngram\": \"these performances\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was an honor for me to get to go there and play on this.\\\"\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an honor\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leisring then leveraged his personal opportunity to pursue his mission as associate dean - extending the KU School of Music's relations with university-level yet freestanding conservatories in Europe and elsewhere.\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3461, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his personal opportunity\", \"from\": 3271, \"to\": 3295}, {\"ngram\": \"his mission\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3317}, {\"ngram\": \"Music\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"university-level\", \"from\": 3388, \"to\": 3404}, {\"ngram\": \"conservatories\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3436}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the focus of his sabbatical year.\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the focus\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3476}, {\"ngram\": \"his sabbatical year\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I visited seven or eight conservatories this year already, just trying to make personal student and faculty connections,\\\" Leisring said.\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3639, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"seven or eight conservatories\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3542}, {\"ngram\": \"personal student\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3598}, {\"ngram\": \"faculty connections\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"Leisring\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were four or five schools in Poland and in Estonia, and I visited several in Spain when I was there.\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3676, \"end\": 3682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.9999870514440551, \"rank\": 1.1575328428850876e-05, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q6